<div class="about-page container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="intro">
        <p>Welcome to The Purr-fect Place! We're a family-owned pet shop with a passion for bringing furry friends and their humans together. Whether you're looking for a playful puppy or a cuddly kitten, we've got the perfect companion for you!</p>
    </section>

    <!-- History Section -->
    <section class="history">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2023, The Purr-fect Place started as a small local pet store in the heart of the city. Our founders, Fatima Sohail and Ayman Najmuddin, grew up surrounded by animals, and from a young age, they knew that they wanted to create a space where people could find love and companionship through pets.</p>
        <p>After years of hard work and dedication, we expanded to a larger location, offering a wide variety of pets ranging from adorable puppies to exotic birds. Our mission has always been simple: to connect people with pets who will become lifelong friends.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Pet Gallery Section -->
    <section class="pet-gallery">
        <h2>Meet Our Pets</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Pet 1 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="/Assets/images/max.jpg" alt="Cute Dog" class="img-fluid">
                <p class="caption">Max - A playful Golden Retriever, always ready for a game of fetch!</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Pet 2 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="/Assets/images/siamese.jpg" alt="Cute Cat" class="img-fluid">
                <p class="caption">Bella - A sweet Siamese cat who loves cuddles and quiet afternoons.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Pet 3 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="/Assets/images/rabbit2.jpg" alt="Cute Rabbit" class="img-fluid">
                <p class="caption">Oliver - A fluffy bunny who loves hopping around and nibbling on fresh veggies!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <h5> If you're interested in adopting a pet or just want to learn more about our shop. </h5>
